      <title>匈牙利议会投票通过法令延长奥尔班执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/hungarian-parliament-votes-to-extend-orban-s-rule-by-decree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利议会批准总理维克托·奥尔班将其法令统治期限再延长六个月，继续维持权力集中，这使得布达佩斯走上了与欧盟发生冲突的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/hungarian-parliament-votes-to-extend-orban-s-rule-by-decree</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坏兔子在激烈的州长竞选中支持波多黎各激进分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/bad-bunny-endorses-puerto-rico-firebrand-in-tight-governor-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[说唱超级明星 Bad Bunny 正试图通过最后一刻的支持来影响波多黎各几乎势均力敌的州长竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/bad-bunny-endorses-puerto-rico-firebrand-in-tight-governor-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举博彩市场在过去的投票中受到同样缺陷的困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/election-betting-market-seen-plagued-by-same-flaws-in-past-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家长期以来一直热衷于预测市场。即使是像爱荷华电子市场这样的小众平台和福特汽车公司内部的投注池也因其预测能力而受到称赞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/election-betting-market-seen-plagued-by-same-flaws-in-past-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国就欧盟对电动汽车征收关税向世贸组织提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-appeals-to-wto-over-ev-tariffs-imposed-by-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国就欧盟对中国电动汽车进口征收的最终关税向世界贸易组织提出诉讼，这一争端进一步升级，使本已紧张的双边关系变得更加紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-appeals-to-wto-over-ev-tariffs-imposed-by-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 13:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默呼吁世界像对待恐怖分子一样对待人口走私者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/starmer-urges-world-to-treat-people-smugglers-like-terrorists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 敦促国际盟友像对待恐怖分子一样对待人口走私者，同时他试图对非法移民采取强硬路线，这一政策问题导致西方国家的右翼支持率激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/starmer-urges-world-to-treat-people-smugglers-like-terrorists</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:09:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将增加军费以留住士兵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/australia-to-boost-payments-to-retain-soldiers-in-the-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚政府计划增加军费支出以留住军人，这是到 2040 年将国防人员总数增至 10 万人左右的战略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/australia-to-boost-payments-to-retain-soldiers-in-the-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列为伊朗从事间谍活动的公民数量空前激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/israel-sees-an-unprecedented-surge-in-citizens-spying-for-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着与伊朗代理人的战争进入第二年，以色列高层官员对国内面临的新威胁感到担忧：他们的同胞帮助德黑兰寻找导弹齐射和潜在暗杀的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/israel-sees-an-unprecedented-surge-in-citizens-spying-for-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:08:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国审查地方政府隐性债务再融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-reviews-plan-to-refinance-local-governments-hidden-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高立法机构审议了一项提案，将部分地方政府表外债务转入其官方账户，旨在减轻地方政府的财政负担，官员们预示了这一举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-reviews-plan-to-refinance-local-governments-hidden-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:18:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰袭击部署在俄罗斯边境的朝鲜军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/ukraine-says-north-korean-military-attacked-in-kursk-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称，这是自朝鲜军队进入俄罗斯边境库尔斯克地区以来，乌克兰首次与朝鲜军队交战。西方伙伴称，此次部署是克里姆林宫战争的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/ukraine-says-north-korean-military-attacked-in-kursk-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:29:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员们为漫长而动荡的选举之夜做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着结果陆续公布，一些精神高度集中的投资者将密切关注利润率，并调整他们的赌注，直到日出为止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 20:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
